{"type": "article", "id": 39937, "title": "欧莱雅的高端化妆品在中国卖得好，以及，机器猫 T 恤很可爱 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-04-19T03:47:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 248, "name": "COS"}, {"id": 334, "name": "优衣库"}, {"id": 1576, "name": "欧莱雅"}, {"id": 2182, "name": "康泰纳仕"}, {"id": 2816, "name": "Kate Spade"}, {"id": 2835, "name": "匡威"}, {"id": 3263, "name": "Loewe"}, {"id": 14244, "name": "浮华日报"}, {"id": 27421, "name": "Beams"}, {"id": 39626, "name": "ALOYE"}, {"id": 39627, "name": "#FFFFFFT"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170419112709hEGmctpDQHX26dAo.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/retail/exclusive-uniqlo-taps-rebekka-bay-as-head-of-n-y-innovation-center-10869641/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>优衣库为它在纽约的研发中心找了个创意总监</strong> |&nbsp;</a>Rebekka Bay 此前分别在 Gap 任执行副总裁和 Cos 的创意总监，最近的一个工作是 Everlane 的创意总监。她在优衣库的职责被描述为“组建和管理设计团队，管理公司的设计和研发，使纽约的研发中心成为公司全球研发的重要部分”。</p><p><strong><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Luxury-cosmetic-sales-give-L-Oreal-a-lift-in-mixed-start-to-year,817872.html#.WPav_VK758c\" rel=\"nofollow\">欧莱雅第一季度高级化妆品卖得好</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;</strong>欧莱雅公布了第一季度的财报，收入上升了 4.2%。这主要得益于 Lancôme、Armani 和 Yves Saint Laurent 奢侈品部的表现。首席执行官&nbsp;Jean-Paul Agon 表示，这主要是由亚洲市场，尤其是中国市场的年轻消费者在拉动。</p><p><strong><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/retail/exclusive-uniqlo-taps-rebekka-bay-as-head-of-n-y-innovation-center-10869641/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kate Spade 第一季度财报不好看 |</a>&nbsp;</strong>与去年同期相比，销售额下降了 2.4%，净营收下降 1%，到 300 万美元。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>在米兰设计展上，<a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/luxury/design/spanish-luxury-brand-loewe-debuts-home-collection-milan-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Loewe 公布了它最齐全的家具系列。</a>当然，这个系列还是由创意总监 Jonathan Anderson 构思，并由英国家具公司 Robert&nbsp;Mouseman Thompson 制作。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419094451MUWSsf74kVJpXGQl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419094459TXKM4kUavOBetSs1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419094505b256OP81FRmunNDx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419094512ny80RYIWlkurbC6s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Conde-Nast-unveils-first-ever-magazine-covers-shot-with-iPhone-7,817896.html#.WPbbfFK76T8\" rel=\"nofollow\">康泰纳仕集团公布了第一张用 Iphone 7 拍摄的杂志封面。</a>主要用在<em>&nbsp;Bon Appétit </em>和 <em>Condé Nast Traveler </em>两本杂志上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419095337LBUKnTCmqc81MJNk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.359375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/lookbook/cos-2017-fall-winter-collection-lookbook/\" rel=\"nofollow\">COS 公布了 2017 年秋冬的 Lookbook。</a>来看看。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419100338SvGdNK7VYPeHAf9i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.520000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201704191003471bY4COKEcxQ6FoLw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.520000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419100352oeUCwYNmav7cG3p8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.520000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419100358hYIxQW7RbwMzs9J3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.520000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419100405MOm4uwxNTH1pk0SY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.520000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419100411JjQAWB0ly4SGvMbF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.520000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419100418qlbmjaiYNn12ZuKV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.518000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419100423GR3eVE8coAdlz2wx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.518000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.kicksonfire.com/converse-chuck-taylor-all-star-modern-future-mesh-first-look/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Converse 推出了名为&nbsp;Future Mesh 的系列。</a>这个专为夏天设计的系列，鞋面用了网面的材料，有浅黄、浅蓝、浅绿还有浅灰。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419101030m6pJtSb7P9gVBUx3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419101039t0lp7uDGbiI4eREJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419101048zK2ySwn3UFJWxEZA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419101118Fo4V9Q0WKLURrdxq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419101128TaNDOoSU1JfstZIz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://aloye.jp/news/doraemon-capsule-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">日本独立品牌 ALOYE 为潮牌店&nbsp;BEAMS 做了 3 款机器猫T恤。</a>很可爱哟~~</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170419101607UtGR0rYIHubJ9aFy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20